{"tid":1692059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期抗爭] 黃色經濟 之 區塊鍵(blockchain) 政治實驗藍圖","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T03:18:59.000Z","uid":108412,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ca15f120edfa372b5f8b44c23b38372ff9fdc899","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"早前見到沈教授一文 <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2805857146115084&amp;id=223783954322429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2805857146115084%26id%3D223783954322429&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfprbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=33211383\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2805857146115084&amp;id=223783954322429</a>，覺得區塊鍵(blockchain)喺香港依加有非常大嘅潛力<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家都知區塊鍵有去中心化(decentralisation)，加密性(encryped)，不可逆轉(irreversible)等特性，非常適合本次的流水冇大台嘅抗爭運動<br />\n<br />\n故此本人有以下嘅構思<br />\n<br />\n<strong>區塊鍵名稱：Revolution of our times (ROOT)</strong><br />\n<br />\n合資格人士:<br />\n▪香港永久性居民<br />\n▪支持&lt;光服香港 時代革命&gt;&lt;五大訴求 缺一不可&gt;主張<br />\n<br />\n應用層面:<br />\n<br />\n（1）<ins>黃色經濟圈 --&gt; 主權貨幣</ins><br />\n▪由合資格人士以現金兌換等值ROOT經濟幣（如: HK$1兌ROOT$1.00）<br />\n▪合資格人士可用ROOT經濟幣喺黃店(Merchant)以電子支付形式結帳<br />\n▪黃店可以ROOT經濟幣再於黃店消費，於系統內兌換現金<br />\n▪好處: 可防止假黃店(e.g. 需合資格方可申請merchant帳戶)，為黃色經濟圈提供流動性<br />\n▪未來: 可成為香港主權貨幣<br />\n<br />\n（2）<ins>電子政黨 --&gt; 執政政府</ins><br />\n▪合資格人士每年提交年費(如政府稅收)，便可獲一枚ROOT政治幣<br />\n▪擁有ROOT政治幣可於大型政治活動或政策上進行全民（合資格人士）投票，如達一定數目則通過，並獲得由年費所籌募的資金所資助 <br />\n▪好處: 612基金+眾籌concept 但冇大台<br />\n▪未來: 可成為電子政黨或甚政府<br />\n<br />\n本人因工作關係了解區塊鍵概念，但未有有關的編程技術，希望有志之士可共商大計<br />\n<br />\nTG channel: @roothkcoin<br />\nTG group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FWkVnAyRL2WiBO7olklPjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFWkVnAyRL2WiBO7olklPjQ&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfprbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=e09cdefa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FWkVnAyRL2WiBO7olklPjQ</a>"},{"pid":"e6035ac17f80a21347498d70f9129ad578c07266","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"先自推十次(1/10)"},{"pid":"69a8ba8d1444bea0e721032ece04a604628c84e7","tid":1692059,"uid":67655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"貨幣信心問題<br />\n會令好多人卻步"},{"pid":"49b3789f1b72de0f75e177100d57da91e768ea61","tid":1692059,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"你呢個諗法太過完美，冇可能做到。"},{"pid":"f2879bafcbee7c0ee52679f4a0f7bb2fbc05ddbb","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"69a8ba8d1444bea0e721032ece04a604628c84e7","tid":1692059,"uid":67655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"貨幣信心問題<br />\n會令好多人卻步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"冇錯 但係可以由小規模開始進行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953d2b0511478353f1131735916523ed5f2c36eb","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"49b3789f1b72de0f75e177100d57da91e768ea61","tid":1692059,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"你呢個諗法太過完美，冇可能做到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"呢個只係終極藍圖 未必可以完全實現<br />\n但可由簡單做起 e.g. 黃色經濟圈支付"},{"pid":"071a8faaa5017a920e8e7c92ba2f33a87ee5629b","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"先自推十次(2/10)"},{"pid":"143c011495bdbe9bd5d2cf2eae1ce58305c2fb7f","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"先自推十次(3/10)"},{"pid":"35b0f29d17d9884943ebbe21eb7f3646d6375f30","tid":1692059,"uid":108412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:30:44.000Z","msg":"先自推十次(4/10)"},{"pid":"0a88d552b61599009df0e041ab0460